{"tid":1024714,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得 十年前超市嘅南翔小籠包","createTime":"2019-02-16T18:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T03:13:52.000Z","uid":210240,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd61c487b4cdd279167c20c406047ebc8844461","tid":1024714,"uid":210240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"以前呀爺好中意買黎蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裡面啲肉汁正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從呀爺走左之後，就忘記左佢嘅存在<br />\n最近忽然見到，記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買咗嚟蒸，乾憎憎，皮又厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係因為蒸嘅人唔同左定南翔小籠包變咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a462b2d02709c803ecbc5b8cfb25077c2fff398d","tid":1024714,"uid":210240,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1RZziS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1RZziS.png&h=b17aab10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前係紙盒包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1df4954200a182c644d870bc9d24b502e8c829c","tid":1024714,"uid":54787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:55:32.000Z","msg":"係差左，以前個隻一食就知有豬油<br />\n<br />\n而家呢隻明顯健康左同個頭個皮好厚，以前唔係咁"},{"pid":"d9c57a4b85bdeafd59a093d8a2c53337a83e0929","tid":1024714,"uid":210240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1df4954200a182c644d870bc9d24b502e8c829c","tid":1024714,"uid":54787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:55:32.000Z","msg":"係差左，以前個隻一食就知有豬油<br />\n<br />\n而家呢隻明顯健康左同個頭個皮好厚，以前唔係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T19:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想食翻以前嘅味道"},{"pid":"28702e9cc9a82e0e34f43cd6daf781b97c56fb0d","tid":1024714,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T21:38:37.000Z","msg":"呢隻牌子小籠包不嬲都唔好食<br />\n以前係, 依家都係"},{"pid":"32ff0bd2b4e892f1515f9e40c9b2e6bc8e24156a","tid":1024714,"uid":77092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3aa2d82923fa7c78ca1923ec2a349f9c2b83f13a","tid":1024714,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔是紅色包裝？"},{"pid":"8b5aeda0e93f29e10b9c59852fe164817ff078d8","tid":1024714,"uid":85721,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"係啊，依家轉左食思念，好似以前既南翔"},{"pid":"0e4520dd6107c58f0ee17c58b602bcb55abae58f","tid":1024714,"uid":84159,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"原來有人都注意到<br />\n<br />\n大慨2013年前 我每隔一兩日放學都會自己上惠康買一包返屋企蒸黎食 <br />\n<br />\n一包大慨有廿幾粒 我一個人都食得晒 因為真係好好味 皮肉汁都好好味 <br />\n<br />\n咁既價位一個人獨食到咁多粒 係一段快樂既時光<br />\n<br />\n但係好景不常 近幾年唔知咩事 我買過兩三次<br />\n<br />\n每次都希望係上一次買錯包過期or制作錯誤既黎食 <br />\n<br />\n點知次次都失望收場 依加同以前已經兩回事 唔會再買<br />\n<br />\n入面舊肉原全唔食得 唔知係咪舊配方冇左佢地轉左做法"},{"pid":"82b95256f9fd09050f914a6492420fafef0bbd9e","tid":1024714,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"以前紙盒裝一次食兩包"},{"pid":"1ad02c154f76751b7aa16d54144483586541f649","tid":1024714,"uid":210240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"點解會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還我當年的味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7cae45dbf8f363c91c4b67b67466528725c6be","tid":1024714,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"唔好食...好似用啲化學皮咁...啲肉好碎好爛咁...好似食啲泥膠入口既感覺...大陸制造...不了!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0d78775bcb65f7410ee6065ad3357be219a6e2","tid":1024714,"uid":78791,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23285575ca50b4aaeebf9ab57eb92f0e4703ce28","tid":1024714,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"呢隻佢一轉咗公仔出就皮厚無汁<br />\n<br />\n連好味果隻南翔小籠包都差埋"},{"pid":"976611a4b708f893e429542be20627da8c22fe56","tid":1024714,"uid":187489,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8b5aeda0e93f29e10b9c59852fe164817ff078d8","tid":1024714,"uid":85721,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"係啊，依家轉左食思念，好似以前既南翔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"好似係殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca2b25e0f09f9707609048d81cc2e7e0508bf55","tid":1024714,"uid":187212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"我會拎嚟煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197714624d90014a27636b3280a3627f2075161e","tid":1024714,"uid":130642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f0d78775bcb65f7410ee6065ad3357be219a6e2","tid":1024714,"uid":78791,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"字大型d?"},{"pid":"33ecad0a0e6af5d128c8a5b0410c0c4d3f90ea66","tid":1024714,"uid":2377,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2r8re.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2r8re.jpg&h=d54c4bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nthis?"},{"pid":"15db6287066bd022f87b4de2a31f1dc3f22f8b49","tid":1024714,